  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shadows in Silence</strong> – a multiplayer horror game where one player assumes the role of the blind witch Elliana, sensitive to sound, accompanied by her faithful pet named Sharm. The other four players take on the roles of survivors, seeking to avoid a deadly threat and neutralize the killer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/fb77d0bcb840e4171eaeb1561c928eb8.poster.avif?t=1750265036\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/fb77d0bcb840e4171eaeb1561c928eb8.webm?t=1750265036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/fb77d0bcb840e4171eaeb1561c928eb8.mp4?t=1750265036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play as a Survivor</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Try to be quieter</strong>  <br><br>The killer is blind but has a keen sense of hearing. Any noise you make may attract her attention. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/f352ba41871c8677514e3faf76bf78ec.avif?t=1750265036\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras_big/f352ba41871c8677514e3faf76bf78ec.avif?t=1750265036 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't let the killer catch you</strong> <br><br>Utilize various abilities and obstacles on the map. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/c18e851541a45c4dca533b8b5c242f2d.avif?t=1750265036\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras_big/c18e851541a45c4dca533b8b5c242f2d.avif?t=1750265036 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defeat the killer</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repair the sound speakers and start a concert on stage using the mixer console; this will incapacitate the killer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/bb6d50c81dcde716e1dff0d434f36190.avif?t=1750265036\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras_big/bb6d50c81dcde716e1dff0d434f36190.avif?t=1750265036 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play as a Killer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use abilities to catch survivors</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If they make too much noise, they leave traces. Your faithful pet cat Sharm also aids in capturing them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/1178c2cffc1baf2e1c523ae4de424110.avif?t=1750265036\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras_big/1178c2cffc1baf2e1c523ae4de424110.avif?t=1750265036 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Thwart the plans of the survivors</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prevent survivors from repairing sound speakers and operating the mixer console. If the sound becomes too intense, you will perish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/9a2ba65c749b380cad66252fd0738255.avif?t=1750265036\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras_big/9a2ba65c749b380cad66252fd0738255.avif?t=1750265036 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shadows in Silence</strong> – a multiplayer horror game where one player assumes the role of the blind witch Elliana, sensitive to sound, accompanied by her faithful pet named Sharm. The other four players take on the roles of survivors, seeking to avoid a deadly threat and neutralize the killer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/fb77d0bcb840e4171eaeb1561c928eb8.poster.avif?t=1750265036\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/fb77d0bcb840e4171eaeb1561c928eb8.webm?t=1750265036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/fb77d0bcb840e4171eaeb1561c928eb8.mp4?t=1750265036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play as a Survivor</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Try to be quieter</strong>  <br><br>The killer is blind but has a keen sense of hearing. Any noise you make may attract her attention. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/f352ba41871c8677514e3faf76bf78ec.avif?t=1750265036\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras_big/f352ba41871c8677514e3faf76bf78ec.avif?t=1750265036 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't let the killer catch you</strong> <br><br>Utilize various abilities and obstacles on the map. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/c18e851541a45c4dca533b8b5c242f2d.avif?t=1750265036\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras_big/c18e851541a45c4dca533b8b5c242f2d.avif?t=1750265036 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defeat the killer</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repair the sound speakers and start a concert on stage using the mixer console; this will incapacitate the killer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/bb6d50c81dcde716e1dff0d434f36190.avif?t=1750265036\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras_big/bb6d50c81dcde716e1dff0d434f36190.avif?t=1750265036 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play as a Killer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use abilities to catch survivors</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If they make too much noise, they leave traces. Your faithful pet cat Sharm also aids in capturing them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/1178c2cffc1baf2e1c523ae4de424110.avif?t=1750265036\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras_big/1178c2cffc1baf2e1c523ae4de424110.avif?t=1750265036 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Thwart the plans of the survivors</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prevent survivors from repairing sound speakers and operating the mixer console. If the sound becomes too intense, you will perish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras/9a2ba65c749b380cad66252fd0738255.avif?t=1750265036\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2626760/extras_big/9a2ba65c749b380cad66252fd0738255.avif?t=1750265036 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
